    {
      "id": "simplify-scaling",
      "title": "3. Stacked refinement simplify scaling",
      "description": "simplifying N stacked refinements (`Base & {p1} & {p2} & ... & {pN}`) — empirically O(N²); regressions show as a worse exponent"
    },
    {
      "id": "excluded-quadratic",
      "title": "4. Many-inequality refinement worst case",
      "description": "`Number & {n | n != 1 && n != 2 && ... && n != N}` — documented quadratic worst case (each conjunction step merges against the growing exclusion list)"
    },
    {
      "id": "end-to-end",
